 by the president of the united states to the national security telecommunications advisory committee in  and served on the committee for  years and as chairman for two years age  mr honeycutt has extensive executive financial and board experience including service as chairman and ceo of a leading publicly traded technology company and membership on the boards of other public companies he brings extensive financial operational and corporate governance knowledge to our board as well as strategic expertise and skills from the technology industry that we believe can help the company use technology to improve operational efficiency source big  sporting goods corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view van b honeycutts full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like van b honeycutt more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in van b honeycutts network and community follow changes in van b honeycutts employment and moneyinmotion connect with van b honeycutt through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example van b honeycutt van b honeycutts connections  sign up now to view van b honeycutts  connections » sandra n bane board member big  sporting goods corporation jennifer h dunbar board member big  sporting goods corporation lewis t williams president chief executive officer and chairman of the board five prime therapeutics inc risa j lavizzomourey board member hess corporation kevin m farr chief financial officer mattel inc richard r pettingill board member accuray incorporated thomas h patrick former executive vice chairman finance and administration merrill lynch irving w bailey former vice chairman of the board aegon nv susan r salka dir president and chief executive officer amn healthcare services inc arnold a pinkston former senior vice president general counsel and secretary beckman coulter popular profiles s